2cf1d2a4-6312-4cc3-b457-7a4ddfe25746.title: Ezekial Lovecraft
2cf1d2a4-6312-4cc3-b457-7a4ddfe25746.text:
Well hello there; welcome to our little village. Pray, stay
awhile.

options.text: Can I buy some fishing supplies please?
You are a bit too strange for me. Bye.

fccf809c-7a75-4eb5-a290-12204d460157.title: Ezekial Lovecraft
fccf809c-7a75-4eb5-a290-12204d460157.text:
I supply the local fishermen with the tools and bait they
need to do their job.

e322636d-b7e7-41d6-b5e7-027a34158d07.title: <player>
e322636d-b7e7-41d6-b5e7-027a34158d07.text: Interesting. Have you been doing it long?

a11c0103-639f-4715-96b8-6df87fa385b2.title: Ezekial Lovecraft
a11c0103-639f-4715-96b8-6df87fa385b2.text:
Why yes, all of my life.
I took over from my father, who inherited the business
from his father and so on.

11cf9639-bd8d-4756-b1d2-dc81ad8b1cd1.title: Ezekial Lovecraft
11cf9639-bd8d-4756-b1d2-dc81ad8b1cd1.text:
Oh yes, we have a long and interesting family history.
For one reason or another the Lovecraft's have always
been bait sellers or writers.

ee979b32-88e6-442e-907f-59d268625d97.title: <player>
ee979b32-88e6-442e-907f-59d268625d97.text: Hmm, yes well. I'm sure it's all fascinating, but I...

edb95bc6-c58d-43dc-8237-bfb9c371e4a5.title: Ezekial Lovecraft
edb95bc6-c58d-43dc-8237-bfb9c371e4a5.text:
Oh very, very fascinating, for instance my great
grandfather Howard...

ceb56b8b-fba6-4995-b07a-8a97d08a60ac.title: <player>
ceb56b8b-fba6-4995-b07a-8a97d08a60ac.text:
Yawn. Oh, I'm sorry but I really must be getting on. I
think my giraffe needs feeding.

c8d0ce47-2f16-4903-b6db-a834371859a5.title: <player>
c8d0ce47-2f16-4903-b6db-a834371859a5.text:
Giraffe. Sorry, but he gets cranky without enough
sugar. Bye now!

5eae38fd-b28a-489d-aa1a-5bd315d54697.title: <player>
5eae38fd-b28a-489d-aa1a-5bd315d54697.text: You are a bit too strange for me. Bye.

55c51763-fb3c-4f13-93cd-8221bd8fea96.title: <player>
55c51763-fb3c-4f13-93cd-8221bd8fea96.text: Can I buy some fishing supplies please?
